WEBVTT



00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.416
Jesus makes a comment about food. He said,

00:00:04.352 --> 00:00:06.112
My food

00:00:06.176 --> 00:00:08.000
Is to do

00:00:07.840 --> 00:00:09.120
The will

00:00:08.928 --> 00:00:10.592
Of him who sent me.

00:00:10.592 --> 00:00:18.240
And this passage is important and it always causes me to ask myself this simple question:

00:00:18.272 --> 00:00:19.648
What is my food?

00:00:19.904 --> 00:00:22.784
What is it that motivates me?

00:00:22.592 --> 00:00:24.096
On a spiritual level

00:00:25.024 --> 00:00:29.952
And it's a question that I bring to you this morning. What is

00:00:30.112 --> 00:00:31.264
Your food.

00:00:31.200 --> 00:00:33.792
What is it that motivates you?

00:00:33.536 --> 00:00:41.248
deeply on a spiritual level. So beginning in verse 27, just then his disciples returned

00:00:41.568 --> 00:00:44.480
And they were surprised to find him talking.

00:00:44.416 --> 00:00:45.664
With a woman.

00:00:46.048 --> 00:00:48.160
But no one asked what do you want

00:00:48.128 --> 00:00:49.152
Or?

00:00:49.088 --> 00:00:50.976
Why are you talking with her?

00:00:51.488 --> 00:00:56.224
Then leaving her water jar, the woman went back to the town and said to the people, Come.

00:00:56.640 --> 00:01:01.760
"See a man who told me everything I ever did. Could this be the Messiah?"

00:01:02.208 --> 00:01:08.928
And they came out of the town, and they made their way towards him. Meanwhile, his disciples urged him, saying, Rabbi, eat something.

00:01:09.184 --> 00:01:13.664
But he said to them, I have food that you know not nothing, know nothing about.

00:01:13.760 --> 00:01:17.920
And his disciples questioned each other, could someone have brought him flesh?

00:01:17.728 --> 00:01:19.808
Food. To be a witness.

00:01:20.608 --> 00:01:22.560
Often requires

00:01:22.720 --> 00:01:24.256
Willingness.

00:01:25.184 --> 00:01:27.264
To go outside of our comfort zone.

00:01:27.744 --> 00:01:29.216
To be stretched.

00:01:29.088 --> 00:01:30.560
To be vulnerable.

00:01:30.848 --> 00:01:34.048
It takes effort and intentionality on our part.

00:01:35.552 --> 00:01:39.552
Likely will be tired either emotionally financially or physically

00:01:39.264 --> 00:01:42.368
It'll cause us to be weary.

00:01:43.424 --> 00:01:45.600
And it doesn't require

00:01:45.344 --> 00:01:48.256
That we leave where we are and go to another

00:01:48.160 --> 00:01:50.720
A field to do it. It's likely to...

00:01:50.688 --> 00:01:52.128
Something that we can

00:01:52.160 --> 00:01:53.824
do right now.

00:01:54.368 --> 00:01:59.264
But Jesus in this passage, he starts a casual conversation.

00:01:59.872 --> 00:02:02.016
That leads quickly

00:02:01.984 --> 00:02:05.888
Into a meaningful conversation and a spiritual dialogue

00:02:06.528 --> 00:02:10.016
In which he confronts this woman lovingly

00:02:10.496 --> 00:02:12.448
With the truth of her life.

00:02:14.592 --> 00:02:16.352
And he explained to her,

00:02:16.288 --> 00:02:18.208
The gospel, the good news.

00:02:18.208 --> 00:02:19.904
The end of the story,

00:02:19.648 --> 00:02:23.904
reads that she came to belief in him and many in the city did.

00:02:23.616 --> 00:02:24.800
As well.

00:02:24.672 --> 00:02:25.888
Jesus

00:02:25.760 --> 00:02:27.104
was a witness.

00:02:27.008 --> 00:02:28.224
With

00:02:28.096 --> 00:02:29.664
Willingness

00:02:29.312 --> 00:02:30.688
On our part.

00:02:30.592 --> 00:02:33.568
A willingness to step out of our comfort zone, right?

00:02:34.176 --> 00:02:36.000
In an attitude of prayer,

00:02:36.256 --> 00:02:39.776
And certainly with intentionality in thought,

00:02:40.448 --> 00:02:41.568
Our, our.

00:02:41.568 --> 00:02:46.464
Conversations with unsafe people that God brings into our life.

00:02:46.592 --> 00:02:49.472
Can go through four stages

00:02:49.536 --> 00:02:55.968
And we can find ourselves leading people to Christ. You know, we typically start conversations

00:02:55.712 --> 00:02:57.728
With casual conversations.

00:02:58.016 --> 00:02:59.648
Conversations about.

00:02:59.520 --> 00:03:01.216
The weather, the traffic.

00:03:01.088 --> 00:03:02.816
Meaningless stuff, but

00:03:03.040 --> 00:03:06.176
It's stuff that we talk about with people that we really don't know.

00:03:06.336 --> 00:03:09.920
And a lot of times, unfortunately, that's where our conversations

00:03:09.696 --> 00:03:19.616
end. With intentionality, with prayer, with willingness, we can cause these conversations to take a step further to meaningful conversations. Talking about

00:03:19.456 --> 00:03:29.504
Personal issues, health issues, family issues, children issues, things in which you are vulnerable. You're putting yourself out there a little bit. Those meaningful

00:03:29.024 --> 00:03:31.712
10 full conversations can then in turn improve

00:03:31.488 --> 00:03:36.320
Turn into spiritual conversations where now you're talking about how

00:03:36.544 --> 00:03:44.320
You have a common struggle, maybe it's with family or with kids or with your illnesses, and you bring in, well,

00:03:44.256 --> 00:03:49.760
How do I deal with that? you know, I deal with that in prayer. You know, I deal with that by going to the word.

00:03:49.984 --> 00:03:55.232
And then those spiritual conversations can then turn into discovery questions where

00:03:55.040 --> 00:03:57.504
Now you're asking the question:

00:03:57.216 --> 00:04:00.672
Do you want to see what the Bible says about your situation?

00:04:00.992 --> 00:04:07.584
And so ultimately that can end with you leading someone to the Lord. But

00:04:07.552 --> 00:04:08.768
Again

00:04:08.832 --> 00:04:10.272
A lot of us

00:04:10.208 --> 00:04:12.256
We have many,

00:04:12.032 --> 00:04:13.536
Acquaintances

00:04:13.984 --> 00:04:17.504
But we always leave our conversations at simply

00:04:17.600 --> 00:04:19.936
The casual if we are simply willing

00:04:20.000 --> 00:04:21.088
And if we

00:04:20.960 --> 00:04:23.456
Pray, and were a little intentional,

00:04:23.680 --> 00:04:26.944
We can start taking our conversations to the next level.

00:04:26.848 --> 00:04:28.160
To the meaningful.

00:04:28.032 --> 00:04:29.440
To the spiritual.

00:04:29.568 --> 00:04:33.344
And ultimately, maybe the Lord will use us to

00:04:33.408 --> 00:04:35.872
bring them to discovery of Jesus Christ.
